revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Floor_RaiseToLowestCeiling}} {{Special|238|tag, speed|Floor|RaiseToLowestCeiling}}
* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': How quickly the floor moves
Raises a tagged sector's floor to the height of the lowest surrounding ceiling. If ''tag'' is 0, then the sector on the line's back side is used.
